List of available FRED API endpoints.

fredr_endpoints

Format

A data frame with 31 rows and 3 variables:

type

endpoint type: "Categories", "Releases", "Series", "Sources", and "Tags".

endpoint

endpoint name

note

additional endpoint

Source

https://api.stlouisfed.org/docs/fred/.
